modules.description: Handles WebSocket handshake negotiation and message framing using TCP. Processes binary and text data streams according to the WebSocket protocol specifications. Enables real-time bidirectional communication in web applications without relying on repeated HTTP requests.

Provides a foundation for working with WebSockets in an asynchronous environment. Includes core types for managing connections and sending/receiving messages. Supports event-driven interaction through callback mechanisms. Enables real-time communication between client and server with low-latency data exchange.
